 board relationships background mr donald f robillard jr also known as don cpa serves as president and director at es xplore llc mr robillard served as the chief financial officer chief risk officer and executive vice president of hunt consolidated inc from july  to january   mr robillard served as senior vice president and chief financial officer at hunt since april  mr robillard is responsible for financings and continues to direct the treasury and insurance functions  he served as the chief financial officer and senior vice president of hunt oil company he served as a vice president of financial services at hunt consolidated inc he joined hunt in  as the manager of international accounting mr robillard served as a vice president of finance at yemen hunt oil company he has over  years of experience in the oil and gas industry and over  years of senior management experience mr robillard has significant executivelevel experience in the oil and gas industry including experience with project financing for lng facilities his experiences in yemen included his participation in the first oil from yemen on to production the development of  commercial oil fields and the construction of several major new gas facilities he served with the international division of cities service oil company where he held various supervisory and managerial accounting roles mr robillard serves as a trustee of the dallas museum of nature and science he has been a director of helmerich  payne inc since march   and independent director of cheniere energy inc since september   he serves as a director of hunt consolidated inc he serves as director at cheniere energy partners lp holdings llc he serves as secretary and a member of the board of directors at dallas petroleum club he serves as a vice chair on the national board of financial executives international he was recognized as one of the top corporate finance professionals in dallasfort worth as winner of d ceo magazine’s  financial executives awards where he was honored as the outstanding cfo in the private company category he is also a recipient of the  financial executives international distinguished service award he is a member of the american institute of certified public accountants the texas society of certified public accountants and the national association of corporate directors he is a certified public accountant cpa mr robillard earned a bba from the university of texas in austinread full background corporate headquarters  ross avenuedallas texas united statesphone fax  board members memberships directorcheniere energy partners lp holdings llcpresident and directores xplore llcpresentdirectorhelmerich  payne incpresentindependent directorcheniere energy inc education bachelors degree the university of texas austin other affiliations helmerich  payne inccheniere energy inchunt consolidated incthe university of texas austincheniere energy partners lp holdings llc annual compensation there is no annual compensation data available stocks options there is no stock options data available total compensation there is no total compensation data available request profile update   the information and data displayed in this profile are created and managed by sp global market intelligence a division of sp global bloombergcom does not create or control the content for inquiries please contact sp global market intelligence directly by clicking here stock quotes market data is delayed at least  minutes company lookup competitor compensationthere is no competitor compensation data available sponsored financial commentaries sponsored links browse companies a b c d e f g h i j k l m n o p q r s t u v w x y z              request profile update only a company representative may request an update for the company profile documentation will be required to contact es xplore llc please visit  company data is provided by sp global market intelligence please use this form to report any data issues information missing  pl