currently serves as chief executive officer and chairman of es xplore llc a direct hydrocarbon indicator technology company which in  spun out of hunt consolidated inc hunt a private holding company with interests in oil and gas exploration and production refining real estate development private equity investments and ranching mr robillard served as a director and the executive vice president chief financial officer and chief risk officer of hunt from july  until his retirement on january   mr robillard began his association with hun  read more donald f robillard jr is the chairman of our audit committee mr robillard currently serves as chief executive officer and chairman of es xplore llc a direct hydrocarbon indicator technology company which in  spun out of hunt consolidated inc hunt a private holding company with interests in oil and gas exploration and production refining real estate development private equity investments and ranching mr robillard served as a director and the executive vice president chief financial officer and chief risk officer of hunt from july  until his retirement on january   mr robillard began his association with hunt in  as manager of international accounting for hunt oil company inc a whollyowned subsidiary of hunt serving nine of his  years of service to the hunt organization in yemen in various accounting finance and management positions mr robillard returned to the united states to join hunts executive team in  mr robillard was named senior vice president and chief financial officer of hunt in april  mr robillard is currently on the board of directors of helmerich  payne inc a publiclytraded oil and gas drilling company he is a certified public accountant and a member of the american institute of certified public accountants the texas society of certified public accountants financial executives international and the national association of corporate directors mr robillard received a bba from the university of texas austin skills and qualifications mr robillard has over  years of experience in the oil and gas industry and over  years of senior management experience mr robillard brings significant executivelevel experience in the oil and gas industry including experience with project financing for lng facilities source cheniere energy inc on    sign up for equilar atlas and view donald f robillard jrs full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like donald f robillard jr more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in donald f robillard jrs network and community follow changes in donald f robillard jrs employment and moneyinmotion connect with donald f robillard jr through your network of conections view full profile   search for over  executive profiles bio example donald f robillard jr donald f robillard jrs connections  sign up now to view donald f robillard jrs  connections » edward b rust board member sp global inc samuel j merksamer board member navistar international corporation jack a fusco president chief executive officer chairman cheniere energy partners gp llc and cheniere energy partners lp holdings llc cheniere energy inc william l armstrong former lead independent director helmerich  payne inc nuno brandolini board member cheniere energy inc jean abiteboul former senior vice president international executive director cheniere lng services sarl cheniere energy inc david b kilpatrick board member cheniere energy inc john w lindsay dir president and chief executive officer helmerich  payne inc l francis rooney former board member helmerich  payne inc greg w rayford former senior vice president general counsel and assistant secretary cheniere energy inc popular profiles sign up now to view more executive profiles » thomas j lynch executive chairman te connectivity ltd john j kita evp and cfo a o smith carl g annessa evp and coo hornbeck offshore services inc elon r musk ceo and chairman t